title: G5 ADC Main Lf support main !
body:
Hey guys, just looking for a support main thats wants to practice in G5 + Elo since theres only a month or two left before new season. So feel free to add me in game and we can jam a few games, also needs to have a working mic and non toxic and its very tilting if you cant be positive. Home all the time after 6pm and can play till whenever and whenever on weekends.

Thanks guys !

replies.body: Heyo  s3 supp main ( but can play all lanes and jg minus top {{sticker:sg-soraka}}  )  at the moment. I play a ton of different supps so hmu if ya wanna {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
